//NAME
<jaN0001>Shuhei
<enN0001>Shuhei

///================================================================================

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0001>"!?"
<enT0001>"!?"

//TEXT
<jaT0002>The next instant, the air lit with a tremendous flash and a raging blast...
<enT0002>The next instant, the air lit with a tremendous flash and a raging blast...

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0003>"Ugh, Uwaa..."
<enT0003>"Ugh, Uwaa..."

//TEXT
<jaT0004>The door blew off, slamming into me point plank and hurling me against the wall.
<enT0004>The door blew off, slamming into me point plank and hurling me against the wall.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0005>"(Shit! I have to ambush them, this is bad!)"
<enT0005>"(Shit! I have to ambush them, this is bad!)"

//TEXT
<jaT0006>I regretted not standing further away from the door, but it was too late now. I had managed to hold onto my gun, but with the damage to my body took when the door blew off, I couldn't move.
<enT0006>I regretted not standing further away from the door, but it was too late now. I had managed to hold onto my gun, but with the damage to my body took when the door blew off, I couldn't move.

//TEXT
<jaT0007>My consciousness began to fade too.
<enT0007>My consciousness began to fade too.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0008>"Ugggh..."
<enT0008>"Ugggh..."

//TEXT
<jaT0009>Where are they? I desperately searched for the enemy with my clouded mind.
<enT0009>Where are they? I desperately searched for the enemy with my clouded mind.

//TEXT
<jaT0010>I was already too late. My eyes could no longer see the enemies standing right in front of me.
<enT0010>I was already too late. My eyes could no longer see the enemies standing right in front of me.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>A storm of lead poured down without mercy.
<enT0011>A storm of lead poured down without mercy.

//TEXT
<jaT0012>Nao, Ryota... Those I had to protect, were the last people to cross my mind.
<enT0012>Nao, Ryota... Those I had to protect, were the last people to cross my mind.

//TEXT
<jaT0013>......
<enT0013>......

